  title: Volcanic Upsurge
  description: Survive volcanic updrafts in a side-scroll flight. The player controls
    a hot air balloon navigating through narrow volcanic tunnels, balancing lift
    and drift to dodge walls and lava plumes.
  objectives: "Maintain control of the balloon\u2019s altitude using fire.\n\nCollect
    the key to unlock the exit.\n\nFind the key before the time runs out."
