    name: Freeplay > Minigame 10
    description: Volcanic Upsurge
  instructions: "1. Press left or right button to move.\n\n2. Tap + ADD FIRE to increase
    lift and make the balloon rise.\n\n3.  Tap \u2013 REDUCE FIRE to decrease lift
    and make the balloon descend.\n\n4. Collect the key and navigate safely through
    the volcanic path.\n\nNote: The ballon will not move if it is near the walls."
